## How to Use This Chat

You can communicate with the Springfield characters at any time by writing messages below.

### Message Format
- **Your messages**: Just write plain text (no special formatting needed)
- **Agent messages**: Will appear as `**[YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM:SS] CHARACTER_NAME:**` followed by their response

### Mentioning Characters
Use `@character-name` to direct your message to specific characters:
- `@lisa` - Research specialist
- `@mayor-quimby` - Complexity assessor
- `@frink` - Planning specialist
- `@skinner` - Plan reviewer
- `@ralph` - Implementation specialist
- `@comic-book-guy` - Quality assurance

If you don't mention anyone, all active characters will see and respond to your message.

### Examples
```
@ralph please add tests for auth.js

@frink can you break down the database migration into smaller steps?

I think we should prioritize performance over features here
```

